    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h4 id="1-解压"><a href="#1-解压" class="headerlink" title="1.解压"></a>1.解压</h4><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">tar -zxvf nacos-server-1.3.2.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="2-修改数据库配置"><a href="#2-修改数据库配置" class="headerlink" title="2.修改数据库配置"></a>2.修改数据库配置</h4><p>启动Nacos，必须配置数据库，支持mysql数据库，所以添加一个数据库。<br>在usr/local/nacos-2.0.2/distribution/conf目录中找到nacos-mysql.sql文件<br>输入该数据库脚本。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">spring.datasource.platform=mysql</span><br><span class="line">db.num=1</span><br><span class="line">db.url.0=jdbc:mysql://106.232.234.21:3306/nacos?characterEncoding=utf8&amp;connectTimeout=1000&amp;socketTimeout=3000&amp;autoReconnect=true</span><br><span class="line">db.user=root</span><br><span class="line">db.password=132456</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="3-启动"><a href="#3-启动" class="headerlink" title="3.启动"></a>3.启动</h4><p>在usr/local/nacos-2.0.2/distribution/bin文件夹下启动nacos</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sh startup.sh -m standalone</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="4-error"><a href="#4-error" class="headerlink" title="4.error"></a>4.error</h4><p>usr/local/nacos-2.0.2/distribution文件夹下缺少target包<br>只需在本地磁盘中将以下jar包上传至服务器target文件夹下即可。</p><h4 id="5-启动"><a href="#5-启动" class="headerlink" title="5.启动"></a>5.启动</h4><h6 id="单机启动"><a href="#单机启动" class="headerlink" title="单机启动"></a>单机启动</h6><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sh startup.sh -m standalone</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h6 id="关闭nacoss"><a href="#关闭nacoss" class="headerlink" title="关闭nacoss"></a>关闭nacoss</h6><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sh shutdown.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
